Mollie Harris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mollie_Harris 0 Mollie Harris (born Mollie Woodley, 23 June 1913 – 2 October 1995) was an English actress and author, known for her appearances as village shopkeeper Martha Woodford in the BBC Radio soap opera The Archers.
